(726, 90, 'first_section_text', 'This family business founded in 1902 needed a more coherent approach to its disparate sales and marketing activity in order to retain the support of their exclusive jewelry brands and to increase footfall in their shops.    '),
(727, 90, '_first_section_text', 'field_547f453fdf3ef'),
(728, 90, 'second_section_heading', 'THE THINKING'),
(729, 90, '_second_section_heading', 'field_547f466058a3b'),
(730, 90, 'second_section_text', 'Reviewing their current activity it became clear that they would benefit from a brand overhaul. We developed a USP that shaped their sales and marketing strategy. This led to more unified creative work and the introduction of a CRM programme to support the âYour jeweller for lifeâ USP and to capitalise on the Tour de France visit to Yorkshire.'),
(731, 90, '_second_section_text', 'field_547f46ba58a3c'),
