(739, 90, '_third_section_sub_heading', 'field_547f4c0f10594'),
(740, 90, 'third_section_text', 'With a limited budget we implemented a targeted digital and print based CRM programme that re-connected with existing customers and encouraged new ones to visit the stores. The Lister Horsfall Ilkley Cycle Races were also a great success that resulted in increased awareness and shop sales.         '),
(741, 90, '_third_section_text', 'field_547f4c2310595'),
